filters 
| essql
  query="SELECT host, response.keyword AS response
    FROM kibana_sample_data_logs
    WHERE host='artifacts.elastic.co'
    ORDER BY timestamp DESC
    LIMIT 1"
| alterColumn "response" type="number" 
| getCell "response" 
| image mode="contain" 
  dataurl={

      if {compare lt to=400} 
      then="asset-0a807073-d056-4c7b-9bf4-225b71e47243" 
      else="asset-1343672d-7c02-4402-929e-0f8fef69cddd"
    }
  } 
| render
